{"tid":490951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金仔發惡】核戰一觸即發？《吉林日報》罕見全版刊防核知識","createTime":"2017-12-06T05:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T10:00:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4adc08852ab5247d80b6d298523e1340f4747894","tid":490951,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171206/large/1512536426_70ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F1512536426_70ed.jpg&h=1decd6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼北韓上星期再試射導彈後，朝鮮半島局勢再趨緊張，甚至被外界估計核戰一觸即發。位於中朝邊境的吉林省，當地《吉林日報》竟罕見在全版刊登談一篇名為《核武器常識及其防護》文章。<br />\n<br />\n文章中，未有解釋刊登文章的原因，只直接講述核武的基本知識，例如核武殺傷力、輻射威力等，繼而再列出防護方法。報道內容非常詳細。未知當時有關方面是否收到特別消息，預早向民眾講述核資料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171206/57547219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57547219&d=Wq1B2vxQIxiLuW1rWFbBr%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=fe7ba18a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57547219&h=de597b27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171206/57547219</a>"},{"pid":"99aa7ac2dfe02cffecd2e19501463ca2493924b8","tid":490951,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:18:39.000Z","msg":"有冇一份睇下"},{"pid":"4b8cf512972c25add3d6ded624d41124dc03b5d3","tid":490951,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88767737876e3fd20e1fe62ddbfefb5d9f8bf626","tid":490951,"uid":42611,"like